headline: Could DoorDash Partnership Reveal a New Strategy for Sally Beauty’s (SBH) Urban Consumer Reach?
summary: Sally Beauty and DoorDash recently teamed up for the "Beauty on the Go" pop-up event in New York City, offering free swag bags and exclusive product promotions from September 25-27. This collaboration underscores both companies' commitment to merging professional beauty expertise with on-demand convenience, aiming to engage urban beauty consumers in innovative, high-visibility ways. We'll explore how this DoorDash partnership, which expands Sally Beauty's direct-to-consumer reach, could...
